<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.2">
<l>kaṉṟuka ḷillam pukuntu kataṟukiṉ ṟapacu vellām</l>
<l>niṉṟoḻin tēṉuṉṉaik kūvi nēcamē loṉṟu milātāy</l>
<l>maṉṟilnil lēlantip pōtu matiḷtiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāy</l>
<l>naṉṟukaṇ ṭāyeṉtaṉ collu nāṉuṉṉaik kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I left all the cows bellowing to enter the calf shed,</l>
<l rend="indent">calling out to you, who has no heart.</l>
<l>Do not stand in the crossroad at twilight,</l>
<l rend="indent">you who stands in walled holy Veḷḷaṟai!</l>
<l>What I say is right, you see!</l>
<l rend="indent">Come, so that I [can] fasten you with a Kāppu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
